"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"My family married me to the edge of the sky —"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Her song drifts from two thousand years ago"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Over the steppe, over the river"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"My dwelling is a felt tent, its walls of wool"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"My food is flesh, my drink is milk —"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The words she sang have seeped into the earth"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Into the roots of every wild poppy"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"I long to be a yellow swan"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Returning to my homeland —"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"But the yellow swan does not fly eastward"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"It circles above the Ili River"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Above the snow peaks of the Tianshan"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"And weeps"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Princess Xijun's song is"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The first poem of the Silk Road"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Written not in ink"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"But in tears and wild poppy petals"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Two thousand years later"}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The crimson Keziaerdake flowers"}],["$","p","23",{"className":"min-h-[