ce"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Had taught him not to trust words"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"But then the southern envoy showed him"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The emperor's seal"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"And something broke inside him"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Like the spring ice shattering on the lake"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"He knelt on the frozen ground"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"And scooped up a handful of Baikal earth"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Black and cold and smelling of pine"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Kissing this handful of earth for a long time"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"His longing eyes gently closed"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"He whispered to it:"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"I am leaving you now"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"But I will never forget"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The sound of your wind on winter nights"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"He placed the earth in his sleeve"}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Beside the worn-bare staff"}],["$","p","23",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"And turned south"}],["$","p","24",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","25",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The flock of rams watched him go"}],["$","p","26",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Bleating softly"}],["$","p","27",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"As though they too understood"}],["$","p","28",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"What it means to be faithful"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Blood-Sweating Horses","》 · ","O, at Lake Baikal Autumn Is Already Deep"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1995"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-6-3","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"Standing on the Shore of Crystalline Baikal / Like a Stern Iceberg"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"annotation-term border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 cursor-help","title":"Li Ling — grandson of the famous Han general Li Guang. He surrendered to the Xiongnu after fighting heroically until his arrows ran out, a surrender that remained deeply controversial.","children":["Li Ling",["$","sup",null,{"className":"text-xs text-gray-400 ml-px select-none","children":1}]]}]," came to see him at the farewell feast"]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"annotation-term border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 cursor-help","title":"Li Ling — grandson of the famous Han general Li Guang. He surrendered to the Xiongnu after fighting heroically until his arrows ran out, a surrender that remained deeply controversial.","children":["Li Ling",["$","sup",null,{"className":"text-xs text-gray-400 ml-px select-none","