ors like twenty-two dark clouds"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Drifting light and swift"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Across the Ili Valley"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Toward the Dzungar stronghold"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"General Zhao Hui"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"With his small, fierce band"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Changed the map of Asia"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"In a single summer"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The Ili, witness to so many battles"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Flowed on"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Carrying the reflection of dark clouds"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"That might have been warriors"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Or might have been the sky"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Blood-Sweating Horses","》 · ","The Rushing Ili River"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1995"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-17-5","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"Distant Mount Gegen / That Marvelous Symphony of Battle Can No Longer Be Heard"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leadi